CatDescriptText: Cutline of possible related image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper July 21, 1951, pg. 24, reads: "Giving Out - Joyce Bryant (at the microphone) show why the Flamingo opening was such a huge success last week. Miss Bryant has appeared in the top clubs in New York and on the Coast... The Flamingo is one of the prettiest spots in the tri-state area. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Woman, possibly Joyce Bryant, wearing strapless dress standing in front of microphone, with man with full moustache standing next to her at Flamingo Club
